==English==

===Etymology===
First attested [[w:1891|1891]], from [[alcohol]] + [[-ic]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A person [[addict]]ed to [[alcohol]].
#:''Don't you know you've got your daddy's eyes''
#:''Daddy was an alcoholic'' - [[w:Starsailor (band)|Starsailor]] - ''Alcoholic''
# One who [[abuse]]s alcohol.

